(42, 13, 3, 66, 2, 21, 22, 'except ye repent', 'Call to Repentance', 'Both passages emphasize the necessity of repentance to avoid judgment. Luke 13:3 warns that without repentance, one will perish, while Revelation 2:21-22 indicates that failure to repent leads to severe consequences.', 'theme', 0.363, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
